  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌍 <strong>Discover the Magic of Europe</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pack your bags — it’s time for the journey of a lifetime! Explore 15 incredible countries filled with adventure and discovery. Stroll through ancient streets, enjoy the aroma of coffee in cozy squares, and feel like a true explorer. Every location is bursting with secrets and hidden treasures waiting to be found!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏰 <strong>Where History Comes Alive </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visit 30 breathtaking European landmarks — from the sunny beaches of Montenegro to the elegant streets of Luxembourg. Feel the waves at Rafailovici resort, enjoy laughter at PortAventura park, listen to live jazz under the stars, and uncover the mysteries of Stonehenge. Every scene is a postcard, every moment a story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533980/extras/75d040b8dcb2d95ff673dc3c7986a42b.poster.avif?t=1772653978\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533980/extras/75d040b8dcb2d95ff673dc3c7986a42b.webm?t=1772653978\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533980/extras/75d040b8dcb2d95ff673dc3c7986a42b.mp4?t=1772653978\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧩 <strong>Fun, Humor, and Discovery</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exploring Europe has never been this entertaining! Solve dozens of mini-games and hidden object puzzles while enjoying a lighthearted adventure. Your playful raccoon companion will keep things lively with jokes and surprises along the way. Gather souvenirs, complete challenges, and relive your favorite moments anytime!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎁 <strong>Collector’s Edition</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For true adventurers — a special edition packed with extras:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 additional locations and a cheerful raccoon companion</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 new mini-games + 12 extra puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautiful desktop wallpapers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Music player with atmospheric tunes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Album with exclusive postage stamps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 memorable souvenirs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements page for the most attentive travelers</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533980/extras/8cde723d21bf354505e7b1e9adbcfbf4.poster.avif?t=1772653978\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533980/extras/8cde723d21bf354505e7b1e9adbcfbf4.webm?t=1772653978\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533980/extras/8cde723d21bf354505e7b1e9adbcfbf4.mp4?t=1772653978\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for a grand European adventure where every scene is alive, every discovery brings joy, and every find becomes a memory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌍 <strong>Discover the Magic of Europe</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pack your bags — it’s time for the journey of a lifetime! Explore 15 incredible countries filled with adventure and discovery. Stroll through ancient streets, enjoy the aroma of coffee in cozy squares, and feel like a true explorer. Every location is bursting with secrets and hidden treasures waiting to be found!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏰 <strong>Where History Comes Alive </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visit 30 breathtaking European landmarks — from the sunny beaches of Montenegro to the elegant streets of Luxembourg. Feel the waves at Rafailovici resort, enjoy laughter at PortAventura park, listen to live jazz under the stars, and uncover the mysteries of Stonehenge. Every scene is a postcard, every moment a story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533980/extras/75d040b8dcb2d95ff673dc3c7986a42b.poster.avif?t=1772653978\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533980/extras/75d040b8dcb2d95ff673dc3c7986a42b.webm?t=1772653978\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533980/extras/75d040b8dcb2d95ff673dc3c7986a42b.mp4?t=1772653978\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧩 <strong>Fun, Humor, and Discovery</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exploring Europe has never been this entertaining! Solve dozens of mini-games and hidden object puzzles while enjoying a lighthearted adventure. Your playful raccoon companion will keep things lively with jokes and surprises along the way. Gather souvenirs, complete challenges, and relive your favorite moments anytime!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎁 <strong>Collector’s Edition</strong></h2><